      <item>
        <title>Git workflow</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[luisherranz]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>What about this:</p>
<ul>
<li>Install <a href="https://github.com/probot/semantic-pull-requests" rel="nofollow noopener">https://github.com/probot/semantic-pull-requests</a> and make PR titles compliant with conventional changelog.</li>
<li>Always do “Squash and Merge”</li>
<li>Remove commitlint from husky and allow any type of commit message inside branches.</li>
</ul>
<p><a class="mention-group" href="https://community.frontity.org/groups/development-team">@development-team</a></p>
