        <title>Git workflow</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[luisherranz]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I’ve done a squash but it’s a shame because the original commits will be lost once you delete the PR branch:</p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/1X/ea40a982ff38b09bf551bb996b8b0a2ca0e471b8.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/ea40a982ff38b09bf551bb996b8b0a2ca0e471b8" title="Screen Shot 2019-05-27 at 10.36.30.png"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/ea40a982ff38b09bf551bb996b8b0a2ca0e471b8_2_690x246.png" alt="30" width="690" height="246" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/ea40a982ff38b09bf551bb996b8b0a2ca0e471b8_2_690x246.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/1X/ea40a982ff38b09bf551bb996b8b0a2ca0e471b8.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/1X/ea40a982ff38b09bf551bb996b8b0a2ca0e471b8.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/ea40a982ff38b09bf551bb996b8b0a2ca0e471b8_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>For really long and complex PRs you lose the ability to see the progress and individual file changes.</p>
